301
00:20:03,936 --> 00:20:05,404
Aquí tienes tu regalo.

302
00:20:05,404 --> 00:20:07,005
Wow, gracias.

303
00:20:07,005 --> 00:20:08,173
Aquí tienes, Kenta.

304
00:20:08,173 --> 00:20:08,840
Gracias.

305
00:20:08,840 --> 00:20:10,808
¡Qué interesante!

306
00:20:12,044 --> 00:20:14,346
